data.description: Welcome Home! Come in and take a look at this renovated home on a beautiful, and quite block in West Oak Lane. Almost every feature has been improved,  or updated providing a desirous homeowner with a spacious, bright, and open home to enjoy for many years. Beautiful hardwood parquet floors have been refinished, fresh paint throughout the entire home, and a brand new kitchen with appliances, and breakfast bar. Individual living room, and dining rooms with new recessed lighting for your family to gather and dine.  Walk downstairs into a new finished, full size basement with new flooring, and new full bath proving yet another entertaining space for your enjoyment with friends and family. The second floor boasts three bedrooms, and a fully renovated full bath.   We even freshened up the front with some new landscaping. Come on in and take a look.
